{"tid":2010542,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人的邏輯缺憾?","createTime":"2020-05-10T13:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T14:04:29.000Z","uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bde1aceabb6750751b78002ec598f381802308cd","tid":2010542,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:08:31.000Z","msg":"有條村有個飛髮佬，專為唔刮so的人刮so。<br />\n<br />\n問：如果他自己唔刮so，他就要為自己刮so；但如果他為自己刮so，他就唔應該為自己刮so。<br />\n<br />\n人類邏輯是硬膠膠?"},{"pid":"9268a3c564fd769d37758a4ced07fadd7c6576ba","tid":2010542,"uid":22604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb46079f15d5a9736bf924f0dde9e4c03732a77","tid":2010542,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"極之1999，我嘗試理解一下<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>前設</ins></strong><br />\n有人無刮鬚=&gt;飛髮佬就會同佢刮<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>情況1</ins></strong><br />\n有人無刮鬚=&gt;飛髮佬就會同佢刮<br />\n飛髮佬無刮鬚<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n飛髮佬幫自己刮鬚<br />\nValid argument<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>情況2</ins></strong><br />\n有人無刮鬚=&gt;飛髮佬就會同佢刮<br />\n飛髮佬幫自己刮咗鬚<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n咁樣係無結論<br />\n因為你個前設無講過刮鬚一定要係飛髮佬做<br />\n只係如果有人無刮，佢會出手"},{"pid":"3ada5e91b52157d43a7838e838a2ae6075d26a6b","tid":2010542,"uid":150216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9268a3c564fd769d37758a4ced07fadd7c6576ba","tid":2010542,"uid":22604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"笑𠹌咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class